The Lock Administration screen displays a list of the current sessions 
in which locked frames exist. You can update the status of this screen 
while it is displayed.

If you are the DBA, you can delete a lock on a session that was abnormally 
terminated.

If you want to know more information (the type of lock in place and the 
frame affected), you can view this information at the MoreInfo screen.

Move your cursor to the session you want and select the appropriate menu
operation.

  Refresh   Updates the lock status.
  Delete    Deletes the lock (only available to the DBA).
  MoreInfo  Displays details about the type of lock and the frame affected.
